Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/dariomanesku/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and create subdirs:

    cd ~/.vim
    mkdir undodir tmp

Setup submodules:

    git submodule init
    git submodule update

To upgrade all bundled plugins use:

    git submodule foreach git pull origin master

